steps for using git-cyrpt 

.gitattributes

1.  Prepare the repo to use git-crypt using git-crypt init
2.   Create file called ..gitattributes
3. Edit the gitattributes file as shown below 
	secretfile filter=git-crypt diff=git-crypt
           *.key filter=git-crypt diff=git-crypt

    above setting will ecnrypt the all *.key files and file name called securefile 
4. Export the symmetric secret key for the repo .
5. Share the symmetric secure key to recipent
6. recipent will clone the repo
7. run gi-crypt unlock  <path of the symmetirc secure key>
